有关军事机关提供必要的支持和协助；六是保守所知悉的国家秘密；七是法律、行政法规规定的其他义务。 国家安全机关提醒，维护国家安全没有「局外人」，每个人都应该参与其中，贡献一份力量。国家越安全，人民就越有安全感；人民越有安全意识，国家安全也就越有依靠。故意泄露国家秘密，北京西城一餐厅负责人被拘"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "248 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/528322211"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkoCN19j2opIdEAMaCDc5Njg3MDIwIPK/6pIGMAM4jAFADXIJNTI4MzIyMjExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1650171796.3782616", "card_id": "Q_524554827", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果我比吴京先出了一部电影名叫《战狼 3》，我算不算侵权？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题，就是在战狼 3 上映之前我先拍了部电影叫战狼 3，我这是侵权吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-f2a59e538e6a1bbec323e079d123f8f4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "246 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/524554827"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIkoCN19j2opIdEAMaCDc4ODQ5MzIyIJbFhJIGMAg4VkAOcgk1MjQ1NTQ4Mjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1650171796.3788552", "card_id": "Q_528151090", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从「神舟一号」到「神舟十三号」，22 年来我国航天技术都取得了哪些进步？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-685a78d4e5216ac98970da6ded057f83_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "245 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/528151090"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIkoCN19j2opIdEAMaCDc5NjQ4OTMzIKq35ZIGMAE43AFAD3IJNTI4MTUxMDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1650171796.379491", "card_id": "Q_66556514", "feed_specific": {"answer_count":